, multivariable calculus,頂多加埋probability,重要著重application,proof講得少,所以唔難讀</blockquote><br />\n少proof就唔難讀...<br />\n相對架姐...<br />\n除左數系物理系 又有幾多科會重proof數..."},{"pid":"7be418ac5d1a54abcb61ab7d7c33b40e9526c71d","tid":244251,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:24:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Engine</blockquote><br />\nphy難d,n展黎黎去去都係linear algebra, ODE/PDE, multivariable calculus,頂多加埋probability,重要著重application,proof講得少,所以唔難讀</blockquote><br />\n少proof就唔難讀...<br />\n相對架姐...<br />\n除左數系物理系 又有幾多科會重proof數...</blockquote><br />\n唔係好明你想表達咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪姐係少proof都可以好難<br />\n咁相對又係相對啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後果句係咪排除左phy因為要proof數太難無比較既價値<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b7f22448cf6d4c3fa6de4c3b82ff4c0ce637d1","tid":244251,"uid":32352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"Quan fin難唔難<br />\n要學stat stochastic process time series<br />\n又要識numerical analysis<br />\n<br />\n利申：19engine仔"},{"pid":"689625dde6eb4b3f49690030e61b1c5fdade5762","tid":244251,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T12:12:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Quan fin難唔難<br />\n要學stat stochastic process time series<br />\n又要識numerical analysis<br />\n<br />\n利申：19engine仔</blockquote><br />\n唔洗proof easy"},{"pid":"1662c99f4777a781a633aadc5a9f74f4ede02993","tid":244251,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T12:17:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Engine</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nengine啲數係多但好膚淺，數學之外，stat同actual science, financial maths最少拍得住。"},{"pid":"d04b8d785b8f3bd6bcfae642a64b7b9c94e35a52","tid":244251,"uid":21623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T12:17:43.000Z","msg":"咁係咁多engine科（EE, civil , mech) 黎講 邊個數難啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" 